<view class="page-shell gradient-page">
  <view class="content-stack">
    <view class="hero-card">
      <text class="eyebrow">复杂交互下沉组件</text>
      <text class="hero-title">{{pageTitle}}</text>
      <text class="hero-copy">{{pageIntro}}</text>
      <view class="action-row planner-actions">
        <view class="ghost-action" bindtap="handleBack">返回上一页</view>
        <view class="ghost-action" bindtap="handleGoHome">回首页</view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <planner-flow
      scenarios="{{planScenarios}}"
      order="{{planOrder}}"
      initial-plan-key="{{initialPlanKey}}"
      auto-select-first="{{true}}"
      bindcomplete="handlePlannerComplete"
    />

    <view wx:if="{{lastGeneratedSummary}}" class="section-card">
      <view class="section-heading">
        <view>
          <text class="section-caption">最近一次生成结果</text>
          <text class="section-title">计划摘要</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <text class="result-summary">{{lastGeneratedSummary}}</text>
    </view>

    <view class="section-card">
      <view class="section-heading">
        <view>
          <text class="section-caption">当前边界</text>
          <text class="section-title">页面、组件、service 的职责划分</text>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="tips-list">
        <text class="tip-item">1. 页面层只负责路由、页面装配和结果承接。</text>
        <text class="tip-item">2. 计划交互逻辑收敛在 planner-flow 组件内部。</text>
        <text class="tip-item">3. 数据先走 mock service，后续替换成真实接口不改页面结构。</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
